{"tid":633804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近3年逾百警員被捕　休班警佔過半","createTime":"2018-04-18T15:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T07:57:19.000Z","uid":20933,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"54f5b2b79ac66885d824b7f9110e0ebe95b5b15d","tid":633804,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180418/s00001/7c44b179c9a87eab1d588ce41c2378a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180418%2Fs00001%2F7c44b179c9a87eab1d588ce41c2378a7.jpg&h=43e07271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警務人員操守近年備受關注。警務署回覆立法會財委會議員的數據顯示，2015至2017年每年分別有35、43及29名警員被捕，當中各年分別有22、23及23名屬休班警。全體被捕警員中，這三年分別有19、34及18人是被警方拘捕。此外，每年分別有16、9及11名警員被其他執法部門拘捕，例如廉政公署及海關。<br />\n<br />\n被警方拘捕的警員中，2015至2017年分別各有15、21及15人，涉嫌干犯警隊定義為罪行性質屬較嚴重的刑事案件，當中19人涉嫌在公眾地方行為不檢／打鬥、刑事毀壞及破壞公眾體統、遊蕩等罪行，有7人涉嫌傷人及嚴重毆打、6人涉嫌雜項盜竊。涉嫌非禮、詐騙或店舖盜竊的，各有5人；涉嫌強姦、襲警、刑事恐嚇或車輛內盜竊，則各有1人。"},{"pid":"547dfde2909a651b014cb1a4ee204482df75c629","tid":633804,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:29:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180418/s00001/1524063240071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180418%2Fs00001%2F1524063240071&d=GKafLAlYqJrlEtR9f%2FxvzV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=07fa45e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180418%2Fs00001%2F1524063240071&h=c8cdeefc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180418/s00001/1524063240071</a>"},{"pid":"ace677c9189b136142f0305ee691479cc294e89a","tid":633804,"uid":5006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T17:13:56.000Z","msg":"係咪咁多紀律部隊連政府部門之冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.g